            "title": "Insect pest management by the horse shoe bats (Rhinolophus species) in the forest ecosystem of Kalakad Mundanthurai Tiger Reserve, India.",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Selva",
                    "lastName": "Ponmalar"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
