            "title": "Vertebrate mixed pollination system in Encholirium spectabile: A bromeliad pollinated by bats, opossum and hummingbirds in a tropical dry forest",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "J.A.",
