            "title": "Chicken or egg? Outcomes of experimental manipulations of maternally transmitted hormones depend on administration method – a meta‐analysis",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Edyta",
                    "lastName": "Podmokła"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
